string:
<noname>Deep inside of
the ocean… We
are born and
grow up there.<fc><f0>

<noname>I'm a Blue
Maomao. My name
is Blue because
my body is
blue. I have a
good friend, she
is very shy. Her
name is Pink
because her body
is pink.

Hey Pink.
I found some
good seaweed.
Let's eat it
together.
<name>UWow! Thanks!

<name>TYou can have
this one, Pink.<fc><f0>

<noname>…Chomp, chomp.
Mmmm… Good!
<name>TPink? Why do you
think our body
colors are
different even
though we are
eating the same
food?

<name>UI don't know
why…
<name>TI heard sun
tanning changes
our body color.
Why don't we try
it and surprise
everyone?
<name>UInteresting!
I want to be
green.

<name>TThere is a
shallow spot
where strong
sun light
reaches 10 yards
north of here.
They said that
the spot is very
dangerous, but
I think we can
get tanned if we
go there. Let's
go!

<name>UOK! Let's go.

<noname>On the way to
the shallows.
<name>UWe've come
pretty far. Are
we there yet?

<name>TWe are almost
there.

<noname>A shark sneaks
up to them.
<name>UHey Blue!
Something is
coming toward
us!
<name>T…I know…
Ignore it.<fc><f0>

Hey kids! There
is a shark! Run!

<noname>Blue and Pink
are swimming as
fast as they
can, but the
shark is
catching up to
them.

<noname>Brown approaches
the shark to try
and rescue
them… Oh No!
The shark
turned around
and caught
Brown!

<noname>Blue and Pink
are swimming
away crying…
They hear the
sound of the
shark swallowing
Brown…
<fc><f0>

<noname>Blue and Pink
had a life
threatening
experience.
Pink looks pale
because she is
pink, and you
can't really
tell if blue is
pale because he
is blue to begin
with…

…Blue? What
happened to
Uncle Brown? Did
he get eaten by
the shark? Are
we safe here?
<name>TBrown was
attacked because
of us! Darn! The
shark was
watching us
swim away.
He will come
here soon.
…Darn.

<name>UThen let's go
hide somewhere
safe!

<name>TNo use! There is
no place sharks
can't go! …
… … … …
Pink? Do you
know a place
called the
'LAND' which is
above the sea?

<name>UI've heard of it
before, but fish
can't live on
the land…
<name>TGrandpa told me
that there is a
place where many
fish live safely
on the land.

<name>UHow can we get
there?
<name>UGet caught by a
fisherman! It
might hurt a
little, but it's
worth the pain.

<name>UOh, OK! I'm
scared, but I'll
try!
<fc><f0>

<noname>Blue and Pink
were caught by
a farmer on the
little island.<fc><f0>

<noname>Now they've
become very
popular in the
aquarium.<fc><f0>
